The paper discusses data warehousing and online analytical processing, which are core topics in the database community, hence cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also addresses security concerns related to cloud computing, which falls under the scope of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The authors propose a new approach for deploying data warehouses in the cloud, which involves distributing data across multiple servers, making it relevant to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses the implementation of the proposed approach, which involves software engineering techniques, making it relevant to cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper addresses data privacy concerns, which is a topic in the field of cybersecurity, making it relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society).
